'''Bernard Senior''' was the 23rd [[Colonial Auditor]]. He was appointed on 1 March 1907, succeeding [[F. R. Ellis]], and held the office until 8 April 1909. He was succeeded by [[D. S. MacGregor]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Former Auditor Generals|url=http://www.auditorgeneral.gov.lk/web/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=88&Itemid=56&lang=en|publisher=auditorgeneral.gov.lk|accessdate=13 December 2013}}</ref> 

